CRITICAL RENDERING PIPELINE DIRECTIVES (120FPS LOCK-IN):
When writing or modifying JUCE GUI components, you MUST adhere to the following rules based on the MASTER_ARCHITECTURE.md:
1. NEVER use OpenGL. We exclusively target the JUCE 8 Direct2D backend.
2. ALWAYS call `setOpaque(true)` on components unless transparency is absolutely unavoidable.
